<P>Help for Distressed Parents. OR, Counsels &amp; Comforts FOR Godly Parents Afflicted with Ungodly Children; AND WARNINGS unto CHILDREN, to Beware of all those EVIL COURSES, Which would be <HI>Afflictive</HI> unto their PARENTS.</P>
<P>By Cotton Mather.</P>
<Q>H<HI>ac Casti maneant in Religione Nepotes, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> Nati Natorum, et qui nascentur ab illis.</HI></Q>
<P>Boston, <HI>Printed by</HI> John Allen, <HI>for</HI> Vavasour Harris, <HI>and are to be Sold at the Sign of the</HI> Bible <HI>over-against the</HI> Blew Anchor. 1695.</P>
